; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;二<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0</span>一二年五月十六日<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 227.7pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 16.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">嘉鱼县市场价格监管年活动实施方案<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.6pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">为深入贯彻省委、省政府关于保持物价总水平基本稳定的工作要求，进一步加强全县价格监管，切实规范市场价格秩序，为县域经济发展营造良好的价格和消费环境，根据《省物价局关于深入开展市场价格监管年活动实施方案》精神，结合我县实际，制定本方案。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.6pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一、指导思想<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.6pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;市场价格监管年&rdquo;活动以科学发展观为指导，贯彻落实国家、省、市相关文件精神，以保供、稳价、惠民为目标，以商场菜场机场（含车站、码头）、药店酒店书店、房市油市银市（简称&ldquo;三场、三店、三市&rdquo;）为工作主阵地，以创建价格诚信单位为工作抓手，以查处重点价格违法行为、规范明码标价为工作切入点，辐射各行业，覆盖全市场，引导创建一批商业窗口行业价格诚信单位，全面引导和规范全县商业行业价格行为，努力为建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城营造良好的消费环境和价格秩序。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.6pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二、工作目标<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.6pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;市场价格监管年&rdquo;活动以&ldquo;三场、三店、三市&rdquo;为重点，覆盖各行业，具体监管行业、监管内容、目标任务如下：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）商店</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> </span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">经营面积小于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>平方米，且不采用电脑打票收费的零售门店。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">监管内容：</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">销售商品或者提供服务实行明码标价；使用县物价局监制的标价签；一货一标，标示内容规范；降价、促销、打折不使用法律明令禁止的词汇语言。</span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">目标任务：</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">商家明码标价率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">95%</span>，规范率不低于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">90%</span>，无明显价格违法行为发生。</span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">监管单位：县</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">工商局、县物价局<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">中大型超市、商场<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">监管内容：</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">销售商品或提供服务实行明码标价；使用县物价局监制的标价方式；一货一标，标示内容规范；降价、让利、促销、打折明码标示，并使用专门的标价签。</span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">目标任务：</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">明码标价率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>，规范率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>；消费者价格投诉渠道畅通，价格投诉及时查处；引导创建<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>家价格诚信单位。</span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">监管单位：县</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">工商局、县物价局<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）菜场</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">监管内容：</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">对菜市场摊位费以及涉及菜市场的各项收费和价格进行清理，重点查处各种乱收费行为；在菜市场摊位推行明码标价制度；每个经营摊位设立一个价格公示牌，公示内容包括：经营摊位编号、业主信息、经营品种、产地、计价单位、单价、新鲜程度、货物存放天数等。</span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">目标任务：</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">落实国家价费政策、优惠政策；以北门湖菜市场和茶庵市场为试点，全面推进菜市场明码标价工作，力争今年标价率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">85%</span>，规范率不低于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80%</span>。</span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">监管单位：县</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">商务局、县物价局<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（三）车站</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">监管内容：</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">车站候车大厅内有醒目的标价公示牌，公示各路线票价；代售保险要在票价之外单独标明，并注明乘客自愿购买原则，不得强制搭售；寄存行李和代运行李收费项目和标准明码标示；车站内销售其他商品实行明码标价；客运班车内醒目位置明确公示本条营运线路各站点起止价目表，并公布价格投诉电话；出租车按计价器打表收费；城市公交车按物价部门核定标准执行。</span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">目标任务：</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">车站候车厅、站内零售商店、班车内明码标价率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>，规范率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>，无擅自提高客运票价、强制搭售保险行为发生，乘客监督投诉渠道畅通，发现问题及时有效查处。</span><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">监管单位：县交通局、县物价局<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">旅</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">店业</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 27.7pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; letter-spacing: -0.1pt; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; lett